node.text: Let's make Vegan Cacio e Pepe with Garlicky Mushrooms! Smoothies have been my go-to morning breakfast lately! 🍹 They're quick, easy, and a great nourishing start to the day. I'm excited to partner with @CaPaoFruit and create a smoothie that's both good for me *and* the planet! 🌎 @CaPaoFruit invited me to participate in their #WonderSmoothie Challenge, which is basically using anything in my kitchen that’s seen better days 😉 (think wilted or browning produce, expiring nut milk!) – and, of course, add my favorite “wondersnack” – a CaPao Smoothie Ball to the mix!  I chose the zesty mango, coconut and cashew CaPao smoothie ball to take things to the next level 😍 I love how #CaPaofruit is dedicated to reducing food waste, using the pulp of the cacaofruit (which is normally discarded) to make a fun, convenient, and tasty treat that can be enjoyed on its own or blended into a smoothie! ♻️ ⁣
⁣
Here’s what I came up with:⁣
• Kale⁣
• Blueberries⁣
• Banana⁣
• Nut Milk⁣
• 1 Cacaofruit, mango, coconut and cashew smoothie ball⁣
⁣
Now it’s YOUR turn to make your own #WondersSmoothie 👉🏻 take a look through your kitchen and see what you can come up with...and don’t be afraid to get creative! You can also head over to the @CapaoFruit page to learn more about their product and check out a fun giveaway they have going on right now 👀 #FromMyBowl #sponsored⁣
⁣
You can also check out capaofruit.com/shop and get 20% off using my code Caitlin20 🥰

node.text:
The kitchen of my dreams is finally finished, and I could not feel more grateful to be able to cook and work in such a beautiful space 😌✨♥️ Swipe for the before! ⁣
⁣
 I can’t even decide what my favorite part is….the dreamy @fireclaytile backsplash, the gorgeous alder @ultra_shelf shelves, or the bright countertops?! Let me know yours in the comments below! ⁣
⁣
A full video tour and blog post is coming tomorrow, but if you have any questions, drop them below! I’ll include the most common questions in a FAQ part of the post!
